posting_body: ['Fridley 2BR Apt', 'Elbrus Management\xa0Leasing | Fridley  |', 'show contact info', '5410 5th St NE Apt 2, Fridley,\xa0MN\xa055421-1178', '$1,095.00 / Month', '- Description:', '2 BR in 4plex with AC, Reserved Parking, Storage, and more.', 'Fresh paint, new cabinets and update kitchen.', 'Many updates, Shared laundry On Site.', 'Pets Welcome!', 'Subsidy is allowed.', 'Qualifications = no UDs or evictions within past 5 years, no felonies/violent or drug-related convictions within the past 10 years or certain other criminal records, must be able to display a monthly income of 3x rent, credit score of 550+.', 'We will review applications with credit scores above 500, income of 2.5 times the monthly rent, or with evictions from the past 2-5 years, but applicants with any one of these criteria may be asked to pay an additional security deposit.', '- Details:', 'Type:', 'Fourplex', 'Bedrooms:', '2', 'Pets:', 'Yes', 'Total Area:', '800 Sq Ft', 'Bathrooms:', '1.0', 'Smoking:', 'No', 'Number of Floors:', '1', '- Terms:', 'Deposit:', '$1,095.00', 'Min.', 'Lease:', '12 Months', 'Available:', '08/01/2022', 'Other Charges:', 'Tenant pays gas and electric.', '$50.00 monthly charge for water/sewer/trash.', 'Tenant also pays $10 monthly lease administration fee and a one time fee of $100.00 due at move in.', 'Landlord handles lawn and snow.', '- Unit Amenities:', 'Washer/Dryer In Unit', 'Pets Allowed', 'Air Conditioning', '- Building Amenities:', 'Pets Allowed', 'Elbrus Management\xa0Leasing', 'show contact info']
